pd_2_com_1text: How do I build a fence?
nd_text_0: Hey kiddo. The name's Old Dan and you're gonna help me.
nd_text_1: I have a great, great problem and I need your help.
nd_text_2: I need you to build a fence.
nd_text_3: Also you need to pay for it
nd_text_4: We're gonna make this farm great again!
nd_text_5: We're going to make a great, great farm.
nd_text_6: That is a great wall! And I didn't even have to pay for it!
nd_text_7: I need you to build me another wall
nd_text_8: That new fence will help me enforce my rabbit ban
nd_text_10: Good, this farm will soon be great again!
nd_text_11: Dontcha know? Press B to pull up the blueprint book, and left click
nd_text_12: You can then rotate the fence with R and place it with left click again!
nd_text_13: You gotta then use wood on the fence to build it.
nd_text_14: Yes you are, or I'll put a tax on everything that leaves your farm!
nd_text_15: Dont you know not building fences is FAKE FARMING
nd_text_16: This farm will be great AGAIN!
